	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Memblers wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I thought the first DW was 32kB PRG and 32kB CHR though.</div>
<br />
<br />Dragon Quest [1] (J) was 32KB PRG 32KB CHR (CNROM), and it didn't have particularly good graphics.
<br />Dragon Warrior [1] (U) was 64KB PRG 16KB CHR (MMC1), being somewhat improved over the Famicom version (one major improvement was having characters face the direction they were walking).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
